– Anterior tarsi in male simple, lacking a comb above the 2 
<superScript id="61A69BBF50495C0FFC0197833497692C" attach="left" box="[908,925,1530,1544]" fontSize="6" pageId="16" pageNumber="74">nd</superScript>
